<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="container px-5">
      <div class="row">
        <%- include('partials/nav') %>
        <section class="body col">
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Clean up on Aisle Me is a 2.5D top down shoot-em-up where 4 players
            run around a supermarket produce section picking up fruits and
            throwing them at each other in an attempt to be the person with the
            least food debris on them by closing time.
          </p>
          <p>
            Four players enter a supermarket produce section and after a short
            countdown, are let loose to grab as much food as they can carry to
            throw at their all white wearing opponents. Getting hit stains your
            clothes to varying degrees based on the fruit with some fruits
            applying effects to their targets like stuns, slows and poisons.
          </p>
          <p>
            Empty shelves pick a single random fruit to stock after a short
            cooldown, allowing players to pick up a set amount of that fruit
            based on its weight. Players' baskets can hold two instances of any
            fruit at a time with the first fruit they picked up being the first
            one to be thrown.
          </p>
          <p>
            Players hit by fruits show visual signs of being hit through
            “stains” (blotches that appear on the sprite) and have that fruits
            point value added to their total. These point values are compared
            against each other at the end of the round and the player with the
            lowest score is the winner of the round.
          </p>

          <img src="#" alt="" />
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
